            <strong>Hey, I am Alex Steiner</strong> a 14 years old developer from Austria and Italy, since I was young I have been passionate about coding and technology.<br> 
            </strong> As a young and ambitious individual, I have been dedicated to learning and expanding my skillset in the field. I started my journey with <strong>Scratch</strong> at the age of 10 and have since learned several programming languages, including <strong>Python</strong>, <strong>JavaScript</strong>, and <strong>C#</strong>. In 2020, I used my knowledge of <strong>Node.js</strong>, <strong>Express</strong>, and <strong>EJS</strong> to create a replica of the Google Play store where users could rate and upload their own games. This project allowed me to practice my web development skills and create something functional and user-friendly.<br>
            <br>
